cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid hexadecimal format 'invalid_hex' will cause identifier parsing errors and prevent proper gNB initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid hexadecimal format 'invalid_hex' will cause identifier parsing errors and prevent proper gNB initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為無效的十六進位格式 'invalid_hex' 會導致識別碼解析錯誤，並阻止正確的 gNB 初始化。
